# Preserve comments

When modifying existing code in this repository:

- **Do not remove** existing comments unless the user explicitly asks you to
- **Do not strip** inline comments (e.g. `# Bytes`, `# Kibibytes`) during refactors, formatting, or argparse→click migrations
- If code moves, **move the comment with it** or rewrite it to still apply
- Only add or remove comments when the change requires it, or the user requests cleanup

Refactors (rename, restructure, change libraries) should keep explanatory comments the author left in place.
